user.biography: Olympic Gold & Silver Medalist Snowboard Halfpipe❄️ Three-time Olympian ❄️ Seven-time XGames Medalist❄️ World Cup Champion

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hannah Teter in Lake Tahoe, California. May be an image of nature and body of water.

node.text: Will never take clear skies and blue water for granted ever again! The smoke filled air has been hard to deal with, stay safe out there everyone!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hannah Teter on August 06, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and road.

node.text:
The first time I visited Tahoe as a kid, I knew it’s where I wanted to move as soon as possible! Coming from the East Coast, I had never experienced such big mountains and deep snow! At the time I had only seen the winter months of Lake Tahoe. Little did I know the summer was just as kick ass;) There are so many hidden gems around here to see and explore. I’m still finding secret spots 16 years later! You know you’re in the right place when it feels like it’s giving you a new experience every year. The journey never ends in Tahoe! Thanks again to @hyundaiusa for the Tucson that’s getting me and my lake day essentials to my favorite spots.

#HyundaiPartner #ItsYourJourney #HyundaiTucson

node.text:
Every time I come to Emerald Bay a calmness washes over me as I meditate on this amazing life's journey; I love the feeling of being completely present in this adventurous moment. Shout out to @hyundaiusa for the opportunity to spend some time with this 2022 Tucson... I can't think of a better vehicle to get me to this spectacular view. ❤️🚙 

#HyundaiPartner #ItsYourJourney #HyundaiTucson

node.text:
🏄 + 🥾 + 🏂 #3in1 ✔️I had so much fun hanging with this crew! And I got to test out the @hyundaiusa #Tucson’s Snow Mode, which is going to be perfect for next winter. ❄️
Shoutout to @alanarblanchard, @jackfreestone, @lukecarljohn for joining me on this adventure! 
#HyundaiPartner

node.text:
#HyundaiPartner - Have you guys heard of snowboarding + surfing in one day? Yeah, we decided to step it up to a #3in1 with @hyundaiusa !!💪🏼 
Watch as @lukecarljohn @alanarblanchard @jackfreestone and I 🏄🏽‍♂️ + 🥾 + 🏂 IN ONE SINGLE DAY! Swipe the link in my stories to check it out!
